column10:
Status 
"In Prep" -  preparing buoy for deployment
"Active" - at sea and we plan to recover
"Lost" - at sea but unlikely we can recover
“Sunk” - only recovered partial buoy, assumed dead, sunk, and highly unlikely to recover
“Complete” -  buoy recovered and data is in house "Unusable" - buoy recovered but data is unusable
column28: Array_name (Array letter + 2 digit version number_Hydrophone model numbers)

column38: Data_End_UTC (defined once data is recovered by scanning LTSA)
